# This repo tracks only the static site/. Everything else stays local.

# Catch-all: ignore anything at the repo root...
/*
# ...except for this .gitignore and the site itself.
!/.gitignore
!/site/

# (For reference, the local-only items currently present are:
#   /.claude/                       -> Claude Code agents
#   /docs/                          -> internal documentation
#   /CLAUDE.md                      -> Claude Code project instructions
#   /prompt-guide-blog-astro.md     -> original spec for the blog
#   /bozze/                         -> blog post drafts
# )

# OS / editor noise (matches anywhere, including inside site/)
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.swp
.idea/
.vscode/
